Thanks for download Ghost Comps

Some thinks should you know

0 - It's document is written by me and my english needs to upgraded.
1 - This is a simple API to handlers some common user interface components like button, text fields, scroll, etc.
2 - The most importante feature of Ghost Comps are, it not is display objects, it just controls your display objects.
3 - Other important feature is a very simple and flexible implementation, just send you display with some instances pre-defined and it is manipulate by ghost.

If you like to visit the project site, report a bug or collaborate:
http://github.com/jancassio/ghostcomps/

Now is that you know until here about Ghosts =O

